sequenceDiagram
  participant S as MCP Server
  participant H as Host / MCP Client
  participant M as LLM

  S->>H: tools/list: name, description, schema
  H->>M: provider tool schema in context
  M-->>H: tool call: name + arguments
  H->>S: tools/call JSON-RPC
  S-->>H: tool result
  H->>M: result back into context
